# Forvis Mazars Styling Guide

Professional, corporate styling consistent with Forvis Mazars brand guidelines.

## UI Component Library

**ALWAYS use typed components from `/src/components/ui/` - import via:**

```typescript
import { Button, Card, DashboardCard, Input, Badge, Banner, StatCard, LoadingSpinner } from '@/components/ui';
```

**Available Components:**
- `Button` - primary, secondary, gradient, danger variants
- `Card` - standard, dashboard, shared-service, stats variants  
- `DashboardCard` - interactive cards with hover effects, icons, stats
- `Input` - text, email, password, number, textarea, select variants
- `Badge` - status indicators with color variants
- `Banner` - info, error, warning, success notifications
- `StatCard` - gradient metric cards (4 variants for hierarchy)
- `LoadingSpinner` / `LoadingOverlay` - loading states

**Benefits:** Type-safe, consistent, maintainable. Use for all repeated patterns.

