## Shadows, Borders & States

**Shadows**: `shadow-corporate` (default), `shadow-corporate-md` (hover), `shadow-corporate-lg` (modals)

**Radius**: `rounded-lg` (default 8px), `rounded-xl` (emphasis 12px), `rounded-full` (badges/icons)

**Borders**: `border-forvis-gray-200` (cards), `border-forvis-gray-300` (inputs), `border-forvis-blue-500` (focus), `#2E5AAC` (emphasis via inline)

**States:**
- Hover: `hover:bg-forvis-gray-50`, `hover:text-forvis-blue-600`, `hover:shadow-corporate-md`
- Focus: `focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-forvis-blue-500 focus:ring-offset-2`
- Disabled: `disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed`

**Z-Index**: z-0 (overlays), z-[1] (content), z-10 (loading), z-50 (modals)

## Accessibility & Responsive

**Focus**: Always include focus ring (`focus:ring-2 focus:ring-forvis-blue-500`)
**Contrast**: WCAG AA - gray-700+ on white, white on gradients
**Screen Reader**: `sr-only` for hidden content, ARIA labels for icons
**Breakpoints**: sm (640), md (768), lg (1024), xl (1280)
**Mobile-First**: `flex-col md:flex-row`, `grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2`

## Key Principles

**Component-First Approach:**
- ✅ **ALWAYS** use `/src/components/ui/` components (Button, Card, DashboardCard, Input, Badge, Banner, StatCard, Loading)
- ❌ NO legacy CSS classes (`.btn-primary`, `.card`, etc.) - DEPRECATED
- ❌ NO manual styling for common patterns

**When to Use Inline Styles:**
- Gradients (not in Tailwind)
- Brand hex colors (#2E5AAC, #C7B179, #88815E, #DC2626)
- Emphasis borders
- Dynamic grid templates
- One-off semi-transparent backgrounds

**When to Use Tailwind:**
- All spacing/sizing/layout
- Typography (using forvis-* colors)
- Responsive design
- State variants (hover, focus, disabled)
- Shadows (shadow-corporate variants)

**Core Standards:**
1. Type-safe UI components for all common patterns
2. Brand blue (#2E5AAC) central to design, gold (#C7B179, #88815E) for premium accents
3. Gradients for visual hierarchy (darker = more important)
4. White text on all gradients
5. Standard spacing scale (4, 8, 12, 16, 24, 32px)
6. Corporate shadows only (`shadow-corporate` variants)
7. 200ms transitions for dashboard interactions
8. Focus rings required for accessibility
9. Mobile-first responsive design
10. `space-y-6` for page section spacing

**Avoid:**
- Custom button/card/input markup (use components)
- Black text on gradients
- Arbitrary spacing values
- Default Tailwind shadows
- Inconsistent transitions
- Missing focus states

## Dashboard Patterns

**Card Interactions** (handled by DashboardCard component):
- Light gradient base (#F0F7FD → #E0EDFB)
- Subtle hover overlay (rgba opacity 0.06-0.08)
- Icon scale (110%) + arrow fade-in on hover
- Title color change (gray-900 → blue-600)
- Shadow elevation (corporate → corporate-md)
- 200ms transitions

**Stats Display:**
- Use `<StatCard>` with `gradientVariant={1-4}` for hierarchy
- Grid: `grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-3`
- Inline stats: `text-2xl font-bold` + `text-forvis-blue-600` (primary) or `text-forvis-gray-900` (secondary)

**Page Structure:**
- Layout: `min-h-screen bg-forvis-gray-50` with `max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8`
- Sections: `space-y-6` for vertical spacing
- Headers: See Layout & Spacing section for patterns
